e ordering link and contact details are consistent across Google and Square.</p><p><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/newcastle-restaurant-square-setup/\">View the Full Square Setup Package</a></p><!-- /AI_SLOT:BODY --><!-- AI_SLOT:SCHEMA -->",
